              patterns of protection, celebration, and beauty. These patterns were not random. Each carried 
              meaning: a story of belonging, of love, of courage.
            </p>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-6">
              When translated into chains, these markings became wearable for our time.
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-neutral-600 mb-6 space-y-2">
              <li>The central piece on the nose echoes the center of tribal drawings.</li>
              <li>The chains extending toward the ears remind us of ritual earrings and sacred symmetry.</li>
              <li>The delicate attachments (feathers, leaves, crystals, geometric forms) connect the body to nature.</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-6">
              This is not nostalgia‚Äîit is rebirth. Rediant jewelry revives ancient imagery and gives it a 
              contemporary pulse, alive in the urban rhythm of now.
            </p>
